To debug a program with [[acid]]:

\begin{verbatim}
$ acid /bin/ls
/bin/ls:386 plan 9 executable
/lib/acid/port
/lib/acid/386
acid: bpset(main)
acid: cont()
myprogram 1234: breakpoint  main+0x0
acid: stk()
main() /usr/myprogram.c:12
acid:
\end{verbatim}


